ni tükühitiirie tüiguire tha x2.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ÜKUMIO</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ükumio igürü kwa Ngai na üiguani gükü thi,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa andü othe a wendi mwega ni tügügükumia x2.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tügügükumia Mwathani, na ni tügükügooca, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni tügügütiia tükügathiririe.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ükumio igürü kwa Ngai na üiguani gükü thi,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa andü othe a wendi mwega ni tügügükumia x2.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Baba twakügaatha ni ündü, wa ükaru waku müingi, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani münene igürü Ngai kihoti.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ükumio igürü kwa Ngai na üiguani gükü thi,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa andü othe a wendi mwega ni tügügükumia x2.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani Mwana wa mümwe, Mwathani Yesu Kristü,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani ndürüme ya Ngai Mwana wa 'the.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ükumio igürü kwa Ngai na üiguani gükü thi,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa andü othe a wendi mwega ni tügügükumia x2.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>We üthengagia mawihia, ma thi ütüiguire tha, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>we üthengagia mehia ma thi igua ithaitha riitü.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ükumio igürü kwa Ngai na üiguani gükü thi,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa andü othe a wendi mwega ni tügügükumia x2.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wee üikaire ürio wa [the, tüiguire tha Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tondü nowe wiki Mütheru no wee wiki Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ükumio igürü kwa Ngai na üiguani gükü thi,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa andü othe a wendi mwega ni tügügükumia x2.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nowe wiki üri igürü ma,
Mwathani Yesu Kristü,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hamwe na Muoyo Mutheru ükumio-ini wa Ngai Ithe.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ükumio igürü kwa Ngai na üiguani gükü thi,</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa andü othe a wendi mwega ni tügügükumia x2.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
