Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Thayü wa kristu ugie ngooroini , miciiini itu na kundu guothe</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Arata na thü ciitü marogïa thayû.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngeithi ngeithi cia thayu ni tugeithanie</s></f>"},{ID:31,
