Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(Kristu Kristu tuiguire tha, Tuiguire tha, ni tuherete tuiguire tha)*2</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(Mwathani witu tuiguire tha, ithui, ni tuherete tuiguiire tha)*2</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>UKUMIO</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukumio iguru kwa Ngai na uiguani guku thi, kuri andu a wendi mwega ni tugugukumia.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni tugukugooca, ni tugugutiia, tukugathiririe </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ningi tukugaathe ni undu wa ukaru waku muingi.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukumio iguru kwa Ngai na uiguani guku thi, kuri andu a wendi mwega ni tugugukumia.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani  Ngai munene, wa iguru na thi, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai kihoti othe, Mwathani we Mwana wa mumwe We Yesu Kristu.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukumio iguru kwa Ngai na uiguani guku thi, kuri andu a wendi mwega ni tugugukumia.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>We nowe Mwathani, ndurume ya Ngai, Mwathani mwana wa Ithe, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o we uthengagia mehia ma thi utuiguire tha.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukumio iguru kwa Ngai na uiguani guku thi, kuri andu a wendi mwega ni tugugukumia.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O we uria uthengagia , mawihia ma thi, igua ithaitha riitu, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o wee uikaire urio wa Ithe utuiguire tha.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nowe wiki Mutheru, wee wiki Mwathani, we wiki uri iguru ma, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o wee uri iguru ria iguru wee Yesu Kristu.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukumio iguru kwa Ngai na uiguani guku thi, kuri andu a wendi mwega ni tugugukumia.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O na Muoyo mutheru, muheani utuuro, ukumio-ini wa Ngai Ithe, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni gutuike uguo ni gutuike o ro uguo.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukumio iguru kwa Ngai na uiguani guku thi, kuri andu a wendi mwega ni tugugukumia.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
