Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni kii nii ingiguthukira na kio Ngai, unjikiire maundu </s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maingi manene, “ngoro yakwa kigathe Ngai mahinda mothe.”</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Thengiu ni thengiu Ngai ni thengiu, thengiu ni thengiu </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngai, ni thengiu we Mwathani X2.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiheo kia muoyo Baba niuhete, ukahonia mirimu riria ndarwara,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>“ngoro yakwa canjamuka ni undu wa Mwathani.”</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Thengiu ni thengiu Ngai ni thengiu, thengiu ni thengiu </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngai, ni thengiu we Mwathani X2.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ninyonete utugi waku munene, Ni uhete gia kuria ona gia kunyua,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nguhingura kanua gakwa nii njuge ni thengiu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Thengiu ni thengiu Ngai ni thengiu, thengiu ni thengiu Ngai,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni thengiu we Mwathani X2.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wira uria Ngai uheete nii ndutage, Reke ngugocithagie naguo Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na nguinagire nyimbo njega cia gukugooca.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Thengiu ni thengiu Ngai ni thengiu, thengiu ni thengiu Ngai,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni thengiu we Mwathani X2.</s></f>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"NI KII INGIGUTHUKIRA (ATM 185/20-D)
