(ATM 29-C/165)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tuikururkirie, tuikurukirie Kristu tuikurukirie Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kristu ndugatutige ta ciana cia nguriai tuikurukirie Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Muoyo werire arutwo aku thutha wa kuriuka gwaku tuikurukirie Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ati wambata iguru, we ni ukamaikurukiria tuikurukirie Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Muoyo Mutheru muteithia niwe o na ithui turahoya tuikurukirie Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ooke niguo atuhe uugi o hamwe na ukurani tuikurukirie Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Oke atuhe utaari o hamwe na umiririru tuikurukirie Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atuhe umenyi, gitio o na witigiri Ngai tuikurukirie Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Muoyo wa gutuhe rwendo Muoyo wa utuuro mweru tuikurukirie Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Muoyo wa gutuhe utheri Muoyo wa gutuhe thayu tuikurukirie Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Muoyo wa gutuhe utugi Muoyo wa ukiriria tuikurukirie Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ooke atugirie maithori atuhe ucamba wa muoyo tuikurukirie Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tutari na hinya wake, tutingitoria rugendo tuikurukirie Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kuria kuri na minoga,twahoya atuhe uhuruko tuikurukirie Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"}],
